## Bug ID: BUG-CRM-001
Title: Template content not inserted into Recruitment Strategy field
Related Test Case: TC-CRM-001
## Steps to Reproduce:
  1. Login as RCM user
  2. Navigate to ActivityMobile and open 'Recruitment Strategy' field
  3. Select template and click insert
## Expected: Field should populate with template content
Actual: Field remains empty after clicking insert
Severity: High
Status: Open
Environment: Simulated Salesforce (Trailhead), Desktop
